events.name: 移動（ラストダンジョン４）

parameters: Sylvia: Luuna is pushing her... No way... That Lucia is...
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] Ugh... It's not over yet... the match isn't finished.
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] You still haven't surpassed me. The real battle starts now.

\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] That power is too dangerous. Luuna, I will have to seal it
again.
Sylvia: Lucia!!? What are you doing!?
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Lucia...what a disgraceful way to win...!
Sylvia: We did it. She's on the brink of death.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] You, I will not let live...haah haah...
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] But...I'll make you suffer a fate worse than death.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Did you enjoy the hamburgers made from those children's flesh?
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Since you seem to like hamburgers so much...
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] I'll let you taste my special homemade burger.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Here, enjoy my special homemade burger.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] You should experience the agony those children went through!
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Continue living with that hideous face!
Hilda: My face is melting---...!!! Aaaaaaaahhhhhhhhhh!!!!

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] The pain on your face will last a lifetime. Continue living
with that hideous face!

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] One less to deal with. The real battle starts now. My strength
is returning. Ugh...
Zena: To think the generals of Valentia would expose such disgrace.

Zena: Lucia and Sylvia, of all people, to be seen in such a pathetic
state.
Zena: I've come to lecture and advise.

Zena: I can't imagine you guys being defeated, but it would be
troublesome if Luuna escapes and joins forces with Regnus Grahardt.

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] (I see... There are rumors that Zena once defeated Regnus
Grahardt. Luca-san denied the rumors, though...)

Zena: So you're Luuna. There was a time when you were hailed as the
genius magician of Jupiterino.

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Zena... the shady prince of Valentia, I never expected you to
show up here.
